PrecisAppointment of DOUGLAS C. STANLEY, of Rothesay, New Brunswick, as a governor of the Council of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety being the nominee of the Lieutenant Governor in Council of the Province of New Brunswick to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Tom Calkin.
